# Bug 01: UI arrow misalignment in generator cards

## Description
An arrow icon in one of the generator cards is not aligned consistently with other cards. Instead of matching the design pattern used across the section, it appears visually shifted.

## Steps to reproduce
1. Open the main page
2. Scroll to the “Functions / Generators” section
3. Compare multiple generator cards

## Actual result
Arrow icon is visually misaligned compared to other cards and breaks UI consistency.

## Expected result
All generator cards should have consistent layout and aligned UI elements.

## Environment
- Chrome (Desktop)
- Windows

## Severity
Low / UI issue

